          "type": "text",
          "text": "Payment Lounge Integration in Finverse - SOP"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. We have recently integrated Payment Lounge with Finverse, where customer payments"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "towards Processing fees will be routed through Payment lounge."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. At Sourcing stage, Sales team to continue existing process, of triggering payment link to the"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "customer. Sourcing"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "→"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Review Eligibility"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "→"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Trigger link"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "file": "/media/Payment_Lounge_Integration_in_Finverse_SOP/images/page1_img1.jpeg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
